# Testing Conventions

## Unit Tests

```bash
make test_provider
```

Runs `go test -short` in the provider directory.

## E2E Tests

```bash
# All e2e tests
make test

# Specific test
cd examples && go test -v -run TestUrlFilteringRule -tags=all -timeout 2h
```

## Required Environment Variables

- `ZSCALER_CLIENT_ID`
- `ZSCALER_CLIENT_SECRET`
- `ZSCALER_VANITY_DOMAIN`
- `ZSCALER_CLOUD`

## E2E Test Pattern

Tests are in `tests/` with build tag `//go:build !unit`. Each test file follows:

```go
//go:build !unit

package tests

func TestResourceName(t *testing.T) {
    // Setup, create resource, verify, cleanup
}
```

## License Header

All test files use the MIT license header.
